      "bullets": [
        "IETF is transitioning RFC authoring from legacy plain text and XMLv2 to modern formats like semantic HTML, SVG, and PDF/A.",
        "Authors increasingly use Markdown tools like `kramdown-rfc` and GitHub-based version control for collaborative editing and automated IETF draft submissions.",
        "The toolchain upgrade relies on Python-based `xml2rfc` version 3 engines to generate responsive, accessible web formats alongside traditional outputs."
      ]
